OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome showery
OL,6,Frain spreading east this evening,
OL,7,Fmainly across the west with some high
OL,8,Fground snow. Becoming dry with clear
OL,9,Fperiods during the early hours. Cold
OL,10,Fwith some frost.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FDry in the morning with some
OL,13,Fearly sunshine. Dry and cloudier in
OL,14,Fthe afternoon, patchy rain spreading
OL,15,Fnortheast in the evening along with
OL,16,Fstrengthening southeasterly winds.
OL,17,FRather cold.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
