OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry with sunny intervals and just a
OL,7,Ffew showers on Saturday. More in the
OL,8,Fway of showers on Sunday and Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
